{"tid":588254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［見報了］連登仔瘋狂開po吹捧莊思敏！！！","createTime":"2018-03-11T05:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:08:54.000Z","uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d96aaf1debea7ccdd4692824acd88c33990b7226","tid":588254,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"最近喺討論區入面就有位網民日日出PO講莊思敏，以往講親莊思敏啲po，好多都係恥笑居多同一大堆負皮，不過呢位網民對莊思敏嘅傾慕，真係令《壹》仔都感到動容!<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前就有網民開po，佢更用敏敏去稱呼對方，話敏敏用心去工作，默默付出，但係香港觀眾就揮霍佢嘅青春，冇諗過點為佢付出。除此之外，佢仲話自己係13年一個晚上睇緊大台播出嘅《好心作怪》，當時莊思敏只係喺戲入面出現過幾次，扮演黃智雯嘅同事，竟然就咁令到呢位網民對佢一見傾心。<br />\n<br />\n同時又同一眾巴打分享佢夢見莊思敏嘅狀況，仲話同人哋一齊騎馬行海邊，又讚佢係個完美女神，係撒旦創造出嚟折磨全世界嘅男人。一講到呢度，就令人諗起之前有保險套公司搵莊思敏做代言人，當時唔少網民都話佢一出場，完全係撲熄晒身上慾火，連套都用唔著。<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20180311/575447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20180311%2F575447&d=wnrB4YlbdlhvLVZtTTAyVP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=28b6dcc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20180311%2F575447&h=e41700c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20180311/575447</a>"},{"pid":"1684d6791f46a86a980bfe7167f4f65323e9728f","tid":588254,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bb60036350caaa607086e62f3a07207c5ef645a","tid":588254,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na-cx.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/na.cx/i/4hNPfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna-cx.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hNPfV.jpg&h=d58897a4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n46吋長腿女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d50c13af62c977d268f98548e3372699a42a4f2","tid":588254,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:00:03.000Z",